<p><span><strong>改革不停顿</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>开放不止步</strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong>深圳，祝福你！</strong></span></p>
<p><strong><span>策划、文案：王玥　闫伟奇</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>设计：王墨晗</span></strong></p>
